    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You gather all your rage and power into a single small ball within your hand before releasing it directly toward a target location. The ball then expands, consuming all that would remain within its path.</p><p>Select a space within range. All creatures within 50 feet must make a Constitution Saving Throw, taking 7d12 + Xd8 Force Damage (X equals your current ranks of Berserk) on a failure. On a success, they take half damage. Any space affected by this jutsu becomes difficult terrain.</p><p>At the conclusion of this jutsu, if you do not have maximum ranks of Berserk, you gain 2 ranks. If you cast this jutsu while at maximum ranks of Berserk and an affected creature were to use a reaction jutsu of any kind, you initiate a clash with them even if their jutsu does not have the Clash keyword, rolling your choice of Martial Arts or Ninshou. Any creature that clashes with this jutsu receives a penalty to their clash check equal to half your Ninjutsu or Taijutsu ability modifier.</p><p><strong>Wrathful Form:</strong> If you are currently benefiting from Wrathful Form, you roll clash checks with this jutsu at advantage, being unable to roll at disadvantage.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
